Dallas Mavericks, Atlanta Hawks Win NBA 2nd-Round Playoff Openers on Road

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-05-03T05:19:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-03/dallas-mavericks-atlanta-hawks-win-nba-2nd-round-playoff-openers-on-road.html
Dirk Nowitzki hit two free throws with
20 seconds remaining and  Kobe Bryant  missed a final shot as the
Dallas Mavericks defeated the Los Angeles Lakers 96-94  in the
opening game of their second-round playoff series.  The  Atlanta Hawks  defeated the  Chicago Bulls  last night in
the other National Basketball Association game to take a 1-0
lead in their best-of-seven series.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  